{"tid":2155108,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版國安法】美商會調查53%受訪者考慮離開香港 比例持續增加","createTime":"2020-08-13T13:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T06:42:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"edeb02734c9d658e182bd66c1628d4b65e6fc90c","tid":2155108,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/LRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FLRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=90580ab9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FLRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y%2F&h=c84a0f8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/LRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"5cd0c3c5a32f34b3db4b72bfb164a35d6876952d","tid":2155108,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"美國商會最新調查顯示，在「港版國安法」通過後有多達53％受訪者稱，個人考慮短、中、長期離開香港。美商會指，稱考慮離開香港的比例持續兩個月增加。此外，44％受訪者對香港營商前境感到悲觀，10%受訪者更稱，即使短期樂觀，但對中長期仍感悲觀。<br />\n<br />\n在美國財政部於上周五晚公佈11名中港官員被制裁當日，美國商會由當日起一連5日進行調查，以了解會員對「港版國安法」通過後的看法。自《國安法》通過及更多細節披露後，在受訪的154位會員公司中， 9%受訪者表示考慮短期內離香港，44％受訪者稱考慮中長期離港，表示不會離開香港的則有46％。<br />\n<br />\n美商會由6月起開始進行同類型調查，表示考慮離開香港的人連續兩個月上升，但商會指，要留意的是，逾8成人也是考慮在中長期離開。<br />\n<br />\n近4成公司會因《國安法》撤資離港<br />\n<br />\n受訪公司被問到會否因為「港版國安法」撤資離港，61%表示不會，39%公司表示會於短、中、長期撤資。這個比例同樣在過去兩個月中持續上升，美商會指，考慮離開香港的公司的趨勢變得更明確。<br />\n<br />\n至於對香港的營商前景，44%受訪者表明感悲觀，感樂觀的只有14%。同時10%受訪者稱，即使短期感樂觀，但中長期仍感悲觀。<br />\n<br />\n「港版國安法」雖已實施逾月，但合計多達8成人認為此法含糊不清，包括有56%受訪公司表示《國安法》存在很多含糊的地方、有24%受訪公司則認為此法存在一些含糊地方。部份受訪者更稱，法例含糊不清，就是因為要讓特區政府和中央政府擁有最高的彈性，出發點是刻意和具政治性，以製造恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n部份美商會調查結果<br />\n<br />\n問：自港版國安法通過後，更多細節公佈，你個人會否考慮離開香港？<br />\n<br />\n會，短期內會離開：9%<br />\n<br />\n會，中長期會離開 ：44%<br />\n<br />\n不會 ：47%<br />\n<br />\n問：整體上，下列哪一項最能形容你對香港營商前景的描述？<br />\n<br />\n樂觀：14%<br />\n<br />\n樂觀，但中長期悲觀：10%<br />\n<br />\n悲觀，但中長期樂觀：32%<br />\n<br />\n悲觀：44％<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：美國商會<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------"},{"pid":"639597c05c1bc43872127dffc8299dfd005319ed","tid":2155108,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"edeb02734c9d658e182bd66c1628d4b65e6fc90c","tid":2155108,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/LRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FLRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=90580ab9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FLRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y%2F&h=c84a0f8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/LRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yin0X2K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyin0X2K.png&h=d286242c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"636cc3968dd8343bb619fa8968a5c5a9332f1334","tid":2155108,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"同上次比，升咗成倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853ef1064dced264e43015d61fd4f7c2364f4c92","tid":2155108,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qoCYc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qoCYc8.png&h=7ffec279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等睇邱腐乳又講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f5561ba9f1c385c3b3c6eacf596428e6818d77","tid":2155108,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"放風準備撒僑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm